name: Edwige Fenech (The giallo series)
description:
Hello! How are you?

This is one of my first embeddings. There are gonna be mistakes, I guess.

This model is trained with SFW sources only.

It's trained with v1-5-pruned-emaonly.safetensors. It should be compatible with many models (if not most the models in this website).

4000 steps. I recommend using Cyberrealistic model for photorealistic portraits, though.

If you like my embeddings, you can support me in https://ko-fi.com/punkimaster

About the prompts, I've just copied from some images I liked (i think it was on the cyberrealistic profile). I didn't want to spend too much time on that. So sorry if you use the same prompts.

This is the first embedding from the giallo series (italian thriller from the 70's).

If you wanna see any actress or celebrity, just use the commentaries, please.
